{"tid":2491405,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一度傳被失蹤 「理大廚房佬」被控傷人　還押至下月再訊","createTime":"2021-04-16T09:38:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T12:31:38.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"89ebdb4cb3078272ca797e381dc14cd030d309e2","tid":2491405,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:38:54.000Z","msg":"019 年曾在「理大衝突」留守，有「理大廚房佬」之稱的施漢恒，其 FB 專頁數天前指他 4 月 2 日被捕後失蹤。「理大廚房佬」被指該日在旺角傷人，首次提堂時遭拒絕保釋。他今（16 日）在西九龍裁判法院申請擔保覆核，惟庭上撤回保釋申請，並放棄 8 日覆核保釋權利。案件押至 5 月 14 日再訊，期間繼續還押。<br />\n<br />\n被告施（39 歲），被控一項傷人罪，指他於 2021 年 4 月 2 日，在旺角太子道西近塘尾道交界，非法及惡意傷害<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">梁鎮鋒</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n「理大廚房佬酒吧」FB 專頁於 4 月 4 日表示，「廚房佬」再度被捕。專頁管理員本周一（12 日）表示，「暫時已經用盡所有能力，至今仍然未搵到廚房佬身在何方，但是仍會繼續。」"},{"pid":"f762c133a4c5727584d3b946eb991a82eb4a2d0f","tid":2491405,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:39:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A6%E5%82%B3%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4-%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%9A%E6%88%BF%E4%BD%AC-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E5%82%B7%E4%BA%BA-%E5%BA%AD%E4%B8%8A%E6%92%A4%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B-%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%86%8D%E8%A8%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%25B9%25A4-%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BB%259A%25E6%2588%25BF%25E4%25BD%25AC-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%2582%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%2592%25A4%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B-%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E8%2587%25B3%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A8%258A%2F&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLT%2BQayrLlxBj8%2BPX1Ib8Zww%3D&h=fae0a62d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%25B9%25A4-%25E7%